ActMinistries and Ministers of State Act
SubjectOrder Terminating the Assignment of the Honourable Lynne Yelich and Assigning the Honourable Lynne Yelich to Assist the Minister of Foreign Affairs
PrecisOrder (a) terminating the assignment of the Honourable Lynne Yelich, made by Order in Council P.C. 2008-1717 of October 30, 2008, and (b) assigning the Honourable LYNNE YELICH, A MINISTER OF STATE TO BE STYLED MINISTER OF STATE (FOREIGN AFFAIRS AND CONSULAR), to assist the Minister of Foreign Affairs, effective July 15, 2013.
